trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Button" /> types to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: Expose les types <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Button" /> à UI Automation.

trans-unit.source: The element associated with this automation peer.
trans-unit.target: Élément associé à cet homologue d’automatisation.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ButtonAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ButtonAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control type of the element that is associated with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] peer.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le type de contrôle de l’élément qui est associé à l’homologue [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the control that is associated with this [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] peer.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le nom du contrôle associé à cet homologue [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that supports the specified control pattern of the element that is associated with this automation peer.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l’objet qui prend en charge le modèle de contrôle spécifié de l’élément associé à cet homologue Automation.

trans-unit.source: If <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Invoke" />, this method returns a <see langword="this" /> pointer, otherwise this method returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Si <paramref name="patternInterface" /> a la valeur <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Invoke" />, cette méthode retourne un pointeur <see langword="this" />, sinon cette méthode retourne <see langword="null" />.
